    <mj-section padding-top="30px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text>
          <p style="font-weight: bold">Welcome!</p>
          <p>Next week&rsquo;s DevOps&rsquo;ish (177) will be the last DevOps&rsquo;ish for a while. I&rsquo;m going to be putting DevOps&rsquo;ish on a COVID-19 hiatus. A large part of making this newsletter is reading the news every day. Even with very heavy-handed filtering, the amount of data I read about the ongoing pandemic is far higher than one should be consuming. I&rsquo;m pausing DevOps&rsquo;ish because the news is hard to read these days. I&rsquo;ll still be around. I&rsquo;ve got something I&rsquo;m pretty excited about in the works. Stay tuned on <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisShort">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://chrisshort.net">chrishort.net</a> for more info on that.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section>
      <mj-column width="75%">
        <mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#616161"></mj-divider>
